data.title: THE SHOW MUST GO ON!!! The Afro Peruvian Sextet's livestreaming experience
data.description:
COVID-19 may have cancelled public performances... but not if we go online and play for you there!

Ever seen the jaw bone of a donkey in action?

Yes, it's a musical instrument and you will see it live from the comfort of your own home!

If you own a computer, laptop, tablet or phone you can watch this concert!

The show MUST and WILL go on. Are you with us?
The Gabriel Alegria Afro-Peruvian Sextet is one of the most entertaining bands on the planet...
